{"TopicId":172686,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Target KSC","CreatedByName":"Mark Kerbin","CreatedById":167193,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-19T21:13:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Mark Kerbin","CreatedById":167193,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-19T21:13:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would just like to be able to target runways/launchpads.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be nice if I could just click on the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E to target it. Especially since its now visible in map view.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust saying\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mark Kerbin","CreatedById":167193,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T13:02:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust gonna \u0022bump\u0022 this just in case.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyone have any thoughts or is this suggestion literally too simple and obvious to improve?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T13:20:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlant a flag at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, target the flag.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDrive a simple rover out to the field by the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, target the\u00A0rover.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr use Kerbnet to place a custom waypoint at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is KSP, use your imagination to solve your problems!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Also, yeah; let us target the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E marker, why not?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-03-21T13:21:09Z\u0022 title=\u002203/21/2018 01:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 21, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Rocket In My Pocket\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mark Kerbin","CreatedById":167193,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T13:24:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223329891\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172686\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521638430\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlant a flag at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, target the flag.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDrive a simple rover out to the field by the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, target the\u00A0rover.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr use Kerbnet to place a custom waypoint at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is KSP, use your imagination to solve your problems!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Also, yeah; let us target the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E marker, why not?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut that requires me to do things.... =(\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTks for support =P\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T13:25:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223329891\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172686\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521638430\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlant a flag at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E, target the flag.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you done this in 1.4.1?\u00A0 I tried, and it wouldn\u0027t let me target the flag because of that stupid \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E marker.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI have \u003Cem\u003Enever\u003C/em\u003E had a problem finding the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E from orbit.\u00A0 I hate that little marker.\u00A0 I haven\u0027t looked, I\u0027m hoping it can be turned off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-03-21T13:25:35Z\u0022 title=\u002203/21/2018 01:25  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 21, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Geonovast\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T13:36:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223329898\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172686\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521638715\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave you done this in 1.4.1?\u00A0 I tried, and it wouldn\u0027t let me target the flag because of that stupid \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E marker.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI have \u003Cem\u003Enever\u003C/em\u003E had a problem finding the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E from orbit.\u00A0 I hate that little marker.\u00A0 I haven\u0027t looked, I\u0027m hoping it can be turned off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood point lol. Yeah...i thought you could turn it off? Not sure how exactly though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Delay","CreatedById":173586,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T13:52:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223329914\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172686\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521639363\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood point lol. Yeah...i thought you could turn it off? Not sure how exactly though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can. Move your mouse to the upper edge in map view. You can actually disable the view on every marker, so you can also turn off asteroids, space stations, vessels, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T13:59:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223329929\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172686\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221521640338\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022173586\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Delay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Delay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can. Move your mouse to the upper edge in map view. You can actually disable the view on every marker, so you can also turn off asteroids, space stations, vessels, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, so they added it as it\u0027s own tracking tab? Good to know.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mikey117","CreatedById":169509,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-21T16:10:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m on console so haven\u0027t had a chance to try 1.4.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought they added the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003Eksc\u003C/abbr\u003E marker so we don\u0027t have to plant a flag /park a vessel on the runway?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust seems a bit crazy they haven\u0027t made it targetable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, all that work on mission builder ,and I hear it\u0027s not available on career?\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}